UID:6hPDo1M3dIfagHciTzqSB
SUMMARY:Spring in Full Bloom! A Brunch Celebration
DTSTAMP:20260325T052409Z
DTSTART:20260325T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a delightful Spring Brunch as we celebrate the arri
	val of the season at University House Issaquah. Enjoy a relaxed gathering 
	featuring a full brunch buffet\, festive mimosas\, and the fresh energy of
	 spring. It’s the perfect opportunity to savor great food\, connect with f
	riends\, and experience the welcoming atmosphere of our community. We hope
	 you’ll join us for this cheerful celebration of new beginnings.\n\nhttps:
	//seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/spring-in-full-bloom-a-brunch-cele
	bration/18306069/2026-03-25T00
